OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,FGloucester's MP says he's now "a
OL,7,Fbetter parent" after a diagnosis of
OL,8,FType 2 diabetes led him to lose seven
OL,9,Fstone in four months as part of an NHS
OL,10,Fdiet involving liquid shakes.
OL,12,FAlex McIntyre is in his thirties and
OL,13,Fwas elected as a Labour MP in the 2024
OL,14,Fgeneral election. That Christmas, his
OL,15,FGP told him he has the condition.
OL,17,F"That hit me really hard," he
OL,18,Fexplains. "I'm in my 30s, it's quite
OL,19,Funcommon, although increasingly more
OL,20,Fand more young people are getting
OL,21,Fdiagnosed."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
