OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,FWhat scared him most was the fact
OL,7,Fseveral studies now show that people
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with Type 2 in their 30s can
OL,9,Fsee their life expectancy reduced by
OL,10,Faround 14 years.
OL,12,F"It's the difference between seeing my
OL,13,Flittle man get married one day or not,
OL,14,Fand that massively motivated me to
OL,15,Flose weight," he says.
