OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,FSince the diagnosis, the MP has joined
OL,7,Fthe NHS 'Path to Remission' programme,
OL,8,Fwhich has restricted to him to an 800-
OL,9,Fcalorie diet of liquid shakes for 12
OL,10,Fweeks. He admits it "isn't for the
OL,11,Ffaint-hearted", but insists the
OL,12,Fprogramme is guided by his GP and sees
OL,13,Fhis weight loss closely monitored.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
