OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,F"I've struggled with my weight for
OL,7,Fmost of my adult life," he tells ITV.
OL,8,F"And it's something that anyone who
OL,9,Fhas struggled with their weight will
OL,10,Fbe able to recognise. The yo-yo
OL,11,Fdieting, trying lots of different
OL,12,Fdiets, whether it's Joe Wicks or
OL,13,FSlimming World or Weight Watchers -
OL,14,FI've tried most of them.
OL,16,F"You lose a few pounds, maybe you lose
OL,17,Fa couple of stone, and things get in
OL,18,Fthe way. Life gets in the way. Life's
OL,19,Freally tough for lots of people.
OL,20,FYou're busy, you're working hard,
OL,21,Fsomething happens with your family."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
