OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,FThe death of his Nan just before he
OL,7,Fstarted the programme was something
OL,8,Fthat could have knocked him back, he
OL,9,Fsays, but the "big change" in his life
OL,10,Fwas the birth of his son.
OL,12,F"It's really hit home to me that life
OL,13,Fexpectancy piece. I want to be around
OL,14,Fto see my little boy grow up, perhaps
OL,15,Fhave grand kids one day. That has
OL,16,Freally motivated me in a way no other
OL,17,Flife moments have."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
