OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,FAlex now sits on the Health and Social
OL,7,FCare parliamentary committee and wants
OL,8,Fto use his experience to help shape
OL,9,Fgovernment policy around obesity and
OL,10,Fdiabetes.
OL,12,FDiabetes costs the NHS around #10
OL,13,Fbillion every a year, with sufferers
OL,14,Fat risk of some serious and costly
OL,15,Fhealth complications in the long-term.
OL,16,FAlex admits he was at risk of costing
OL,17,Fthe NHS a lot of money, and as a
OL,18,Fpolitician, wanted to do something
OL,19,Fabout it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
