OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,FFindings published in the Lancet show
OL,7,Fone third of participants with Type 2
OL,8,Fdiabetes, who have completed the NHS
OL,9,Fprogramme he's on, enter remission.
OL,10,FIt's something Alex hopes he'll do
OL,11,Ftoo, as he's about to move onto the
OL,12,Fsecond part of the programme,
OL,13,Fgradually reintroduce solid food, and
OL,14,Fnew daily habits.
OL,16,FSymptoms of Type 2 diabetes
