OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,F"There are so many more young people
OL,7,Fbeing diagnosed with Type 2 diabetes
OL,8,Fand there is such a stigma attached to
OL,9,Fit, and to obesity and being
OL,10,Foverweight more generally," he adds.
OL,12,F"People need to know there are people
OL,13,Fout there like them going through this
OL,14,Ftoo and there is help available, you
OL,15,Fdon't need to be ashamed to ask for
OL,16,Fhelp, and there is to support here to
OL,17,Fhelp you on that journey."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
