OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,F"I don't come from a political
OL,7,Fbackground. I went to a state school.
OL,8,FI didn't go to Eton, or Oxford or
OL,9,FCambridge," he says. "That's not to
OL,10,Fsay I haven't had a lucky or
OL,11,Fprivileged life, and I recognise that.
OL,12,FBut the challenges people in my
OL,13,Fconstituency are facing - whether
OL,14,Fthat's getting childcare or finding a
OL,15,Fgood school for their kids, getting a
OL,16,FGP appointment, finding a dentist -
OL,17,Fthese are things me and my family are
OL,18,Fgoing through every day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
