OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,F"That's part of the reason I stood to
OL,7,Fbe an MP. I think we need more normal
OL,8,Fpeople in politics and it's important
OL,9,Fto use opportunities like this to
OL,10,Fshare with people."
OL,12,FMr McIntyre hopes this will prove to
OL,13,Fbe a good example of shifting the NHS
OL,14,Fmodel more from treatment to
OL,15,Fprevention. He admits he's
OL,16,F"evangelical" about the programme
OL,17,Fbecause it has so far worked for him,
OL,18,Fbut accepts it won't work for everyone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
