OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,FHe's not against weight loss jabs,
OL,7,Feither, but notes they are
OL,8,Fconsiderably more expensive than
OL,9,Fshakes and soups.
OL,11,FHe says the money saved from rolling
OL,12,Fout the scheme could help more people
OL,13,Finto remission, with the money saved
OL,14,Fable to be to spent "on other
OL,15,Ffrontline services" and helping people
OL,16,F"live happier, healthier lives".
OL,18,F"For me it's about being the best
OL,19,Fversion of me I can possibly be.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
