OL,3,C'I'm a better parent': MP with
OL,4,Cdiabetes sheds seven stone on NHS diet
OL,6,F"And that's not to say I wasn't a good
OL,7,FDad when I was overweight, but I just
OL,8,Ffeel I can do more now.
OL,10,FBut I'm really grateful to the NHS. It
OL,11,Fhas genuinely saved my life and given
OL,12,Fme my life back, and for that I'll
OL,13,Falways be grateful."
OL,15,FFor more information on diabetes and
OL,16,Fhow to get help, visit the NHS website.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
